122	   * runner to reach (exact match). Empty/undefined means "no egress" (the
123	   * proxy denies every CONNECT/HTTP request that doesn't appear in the
124	   * list). The dev-agents-stub seeds `['api.anthropic.com']` so the SDK
125	   * runner can call Anthropic; production agents grow per-row allowlists
126	   * in Phase 9.5+.
