232	 * The orchestrator opens a `proxy:open-session` BEFORE `sandbox:open-session`
233	 * (when @ax/credential-proxy is loaded) and packs the resolved endpoint, CA
234	 * cert PEM, and per-session credential placeholder envMap into this shape.
